                            </a>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span alt="공유링크 복사" class="material-icons shareLink" onclick="sharUrl()">
                                link
                            </span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="guest_avatar_title text-center text-slate-500">접속 유저</h4>
                    <div class="none_guest_div">
                        <span class="material-icons">
                            person_off
                        </span>
                        <p class="text-center text-slate-500">접속한 유저가 없습니다.</p>       
                    </div>
                    <div class="guest_avatar_div">
                    </div>
